64	### Clerk (`packages/plugins/clerk/src/clerk.ts`)
65	
66	The Clerk manages writ lifecycle. It validates writ types at `post()` time:
67	
68	```typescript
69	const BUILTIN_TYPES = new Set(['mandate']);
70	
71	function resolveWritTypes(): Set<string> {
72	  const config = resolveClerkConfig();
73	  const declared = (config.writTypes ?? []).map((entry) => entry.name);
74	  return new Set([...BUILTIN_TYPES, ...declared]);
